		<release version="1.4.0" date="" description="OpenLR release 1.4.0">
			<action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="update">
                Improved performance of MapDatabase.getAllNodes() and MapDatabase.getAllLines 
			</action>
			<action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="update">
                Remove dependency on geotools
			</action>
			<action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="update">
                Changed license conditions from GPL v2 to Apache v2		
			</action>
			<action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="add">
                Added possibility to provide map database via input stream			
			</action>
            <action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="update">
                Adapted to interface changes in OpenLR map interface:
                Line provides now methods that deliver GeoCoordinates instead of 
                Point2D instances. The former methods getShape and getPointAlongLine still exist 
                for backwards compatibility but are with lower performance. They are marked "deprecated".
            </action>	
            <action dev="TomTom International B.V." type="fix">
                Removed log4j configuration included in this library which interfered 
                with log4j configurations of applications using the library.
            </action>		
